snippet.title: WAR OF THE VISIONS FINAL FANTASY BRAVE EXVIUS | FINAL FANTASY I Collaboration
snippet.description:
Once again, the Warrior of Light returns to Ardra in WAR OF THE VISIONS FINAL FANTASY BRAVE EXVIUS during the FINAL FANTASY I Collaboration Event!  

Starting June 16 until July 13, 2021, have the chance to summon the limited time UR unit as well as enjoy a login bonus to earn up to 2,500 Visiore and more! 

For the first week of the FFI Collaboration, enjoy a once a day only UR Guaranteed Free 10x Summon and get up to 70 free Summons until June 22, 2021! 

WOTV FFBE is free to play.  

#WOTVFFBE https://sqex.link/2v5
